                                "stop": 11.292,
                                "byte_start": 73957,
                                "byte_stop": 119201,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 90-333, Lampf, Pleva, Lipkind, Prupis, and Petigrow versus Gilbertson will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 11.292,
                        "stop": 130.325,
